00:04:44.580 --> 00:04:47.580
<i>I'm probably just worked up emotionally.</i>

00:04:48.210 --> 00:04:51.130
<i>That's why I felt scared of vampires after all this time.</i>

00:04:52.170 --> 00:04:54.380
