00:05:51.960 --> 00:05:54.290
Well, you gotta be a bit more discreet, y'know?

00:05:54.290 --> 00:05:56.670
Then you look without making it seem like it?

00:05:56.670 --> 00:05:58.670
Oh, I'm the master of that kind of thing.

00:05:58.670 --> 00:06:02.460
I pretend like I don't even care,
but I never miss a stroke of raunchy luck.

00:06:02.460 --> 00:06:03.710
That's super cool!

00:06:04.920 --> 00:06:06.130
Listen, Ko.

00:06:06.420 --> 00:06:09.080
Why do you want to be a vampire?

00:06:10.960 --> 00:06:13.040
What you think of as fun...

00:06:13.040 --> 00:06:15.170
Do you have to be a vampire to do it?

00:06:15.750 --> 00:06:18.380
I know you don't like fitting in,

00:06:18.380 --> 00:06:21.170
and that you were trying really hard
to fake it when we got to middle school.

00:06:21.670 --> 00:06:23.500
You got tired of all that, right?

00:06:23.500 --> 00:06:24.880
I get it, but-

00:06:24.880 --> 00:06:26.290
H-hold on!

00:06:26.540 --> 00:06:27.540
Why...

00:06:29.380 --> 00:06:30.790
What we saw at school the other night...

00:06:31.460 --> 00:06:33.000
That was a vampire, right?

00:06:33.000 --> 00:06:34.880
Th-that's a misunderstanding!

00:06:34.880 --> 00:06:36.710
Or rather, a really unusual case!

00:06:36.960 --> 00:06:38.500
But it was, wasn't it?

00:06:39.670 --> 00:06:43.170
It attacked Akira,
and she could have been killed, right?

00:06:43.790 --> 00:06:45.540
Is that what you want to be?

00:06:46.210 --> 00:06:47.210
Well...

00:06:47.420 --> 00:06:48.830
I dunno about that...

00:06:50.500 --> 00:06:51.710
Look, Ko...

00:06:52.040 --> 00:06:55.580
We kind of drifted apart once we
got to middle school, y'know?

00:06:56.250 --> 00:06:57.830
We weren't in the same class,

00:06:57.830 --> 00:07:00.710
and I didn't want to get in the way
when you were trying to change your image.

00:07:01.540 --> 00:07:05.710
So when we ran into each other for the first time
in a while, I was a little worried.

00:07:06.330 --> 00:07:08.330
Whether we'd be able to talk like we used to.

00:07:10.210 --> 00:07:11.670
But I didn't need to worry.

00:07:12.130 --> 00:07:16.540
I was happy to realize, "Oh, we're totally still friends."

00:07:19.830 --> 00:07:23.790
What is it you want to do by becoming a vampire?

00:07:26.880 --> 00:07:28.170
<i>What I want to do?</i>

00:07:28.540 --> 00:07:29.960
<i>As a vampire?</i>

00:07:30.580 --> 00:07:31.790
<i>Why do I want it?</i>

00:07:32.080 --> 00:07:33.500
<i>Because there's freedom?</i>

00:07:33.960 --> 00:07:35.750
<i>Then, am I not free now?</i>

00:07:36.290 --> 00:07:37.580
<i>It's not like I'm going to school.</i>

00:07:37.920 --> 00:07:39.250
<i>I wander around at night.</i>

00:07:41.040 --> 00:07:42.540
<i>Why did I want to become one again?</i>

00:07:43.460 --> 00:07:44.830
<i>Because of Nazuna-chan?</i>

00:07:45.170 --> 00:07:48.330
<i>No, I hang out with Nazuna-chan
because I want to be a vampire.</i>

00:07:48.960 --> 00:07:50.250
<i>Because I want to fall in love...</i>

00:07:50.500 --> 00:07:53.330
<i>No, the order's mixed up.</i>

00:07:54.080 --> 00:07:57.210
<i>I'm trying to fall in love
so that I can become a vampire.</i>

00:07:58.460 --> 00:08:00.080
C'mon, tell me!

00:08:00.460 --> 00:08:03.210
Are you going to become a vampire
and trick people to suck their blood?

00:08:03.540 --> 00:08:06.830
Or are you not going to drink anyone's blood,
lose control and become like that thing?

00:08:07.630 --> 00:08:09.080
Either way, I...

00:08:10.790 --> 00:08:11.790
Uh...

00:08:12.630 --> 00:08:14.170
You don't have to decide right away.

00:08:14.830 --> 00:08:16.330
But I want you to think about it.

00:08:17.250 --> 00:08:20.170
About what it means to become a vampire.

00:08:21.540 --> 00:08:23.210
What did your friend want?

00:08:23.210 --> 00:08:24.420
Whoa!

00:08:24.830 --> 00:08:26.460
Wh-what's the matter Ko-kun?!

00:08:26.460 --> 00:08:28.380
