00:08:29.630 --> 00:08:32.130
Sorry, Nazuna-chan, just for a bit.

00:08:33.630 --> 00:08:34.830
Just for a bit...

00:08:38.290 --> 00:08:40.580
<i>Nazuna-chan, tell me!</i>

00:08:41.290 --> 00:08:43.880
<i>What am I thinking right now?</i>

00:08:50.330 --> 00:08:54.080
Hey, couldn't we have stayed at your place like always?

00:08:54.460 --> 00:08:55.670
Or somewhere outside?

00:08:55.670 --> 00:08:57.790
Oh come on, just for tonight.

00:08:57.960 --> 00:09:01.500
I don't think there's anyone home, but hold on.

00:09:01.500 --> 00:09:02.330
Sure thing.

00:09:02.330 --> 00:09:04.210
<b>For Meals</b>

00:09:04.960 --> 00:09:05.960
It's okay.

00:09:05.960 --> 00:09:07.330
Come on in, Nazuna-chan!

