00:18:27.790 --> 00:18:29.920
Not to worry!

00:18:30.460 --> 00:18:33.790
Because I'll kill every single one of them.

00:18:35.670 --> 00:18:36.920
N-no!

00:18:38.540 --> 00:18:39.750
You can't!

00:18:39.750 --> 00:18:42.710
I can't believe that those people are really that evil.

00:18:43.210 --> 00:18:44.960
They fret over things just like us,

00:18:44.960 --> 00:18:47.500
and they have something akin to respect for humans.

00:18:48.500 --> 00:18:50.960
They have the ability to understand
people's vulnerabilities.

00:18:51.380 --> 00:18:53.540
Saying that they only ever cause misfortune is a lie!

00:18:53.960 --> 00:18:57.000
I can't agree with your reasoning!

00:18:59.960 --> 00:19:01.210
Fine, be that way.

00:19:01.630 --> 00:19:05.790
